wines_slim = list(
  judge = match(Wines2012$judge, unique(Wines2012$judge)),
  wine = match(Wines2012$wine, unique(Wines2012$wine)),
  score_std = scale(Wines2012$score)
)
  
m1 <- ulam(
  alist(
    score_std ~ dnorm( mu , sigma ) ,
    mu <- a + j[judge] + w[wine],
    a ~ dnorm(0,1),
    j[judge] ~ dnorm( 0 , 1 ) ,
    w[wine] ~ dnorm( 0, 1 ),
    sigma ~ dexp(1)),
  data=wines_slim, chains=4, core = 4, iter = 2000)
#traceplot(m1)
